<script>
// ─── NAV SCROLL ───
const nav = document.getElementById('nav');
window.addEventListener('scroll', () => { nav.classList.toggle('scrolled', window.scrollY > 60); });

// ─── SCROLL REVEAL ───
const revealEls = document.querySelectorAll('.reveal, .feature-card');
const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
  entries.forEach((entry, i) => {
    if (entry.isIntersecting) {
      setTimeout(() => entry.target.classList.add('visible'), i * 120);
      observer.unobserve(entry.target);
    }
  });
}, { threshold: 0.1 });
revealEls.forEach(el => observer.observe(el));

// ─── BOOKING STATE ───
const PRICES = { 1: 895, 2: 1395 };
const PRICE_EXTRA = 499;

// Pre-seeded occupied dates (demo data)
const occupiedDates = new Set([
  '2026-02-20','2026-02-21','2026-02-22',
  '2026-03-07','2026-03-08',
  '2026-03-14','2026-03-15','2026-03-16',
  '2026-03-21',
  '2026-04-04','2026-04-05','2026-04-06','2026-04-07',
  '2026-04-18','2026-04-19',
  '2026-05-01','2026-05-02','2026-05-03',
  '2026-05-17','2026-05-18',
]);

// Load from localStorage
function loadBookings() {
  try {
    const saved = localStorage.getItem('vildbad_bookings');
    if (saved) {
      JSON.parse(saved).forEach(d => occupiedDates.add(d));
    }
  } catch(e) {}
}

function saveBooking(start, end) {
  try {
    const saved = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('vildbad_bookings') || '[]');
    let d = new Date(start);
    const endD = new Date(end);
    while (d <= endD) {
      const str = d.toISOString().split('T')[0];
      saved.push(str);
      occupiedDates.add(str);
      d.setDate(d.getDate() + 1);
    }
    localStorage.setItem('vildbad_bookings', JSON.stringify(saved));
  } catch(e) {}
}

loadBookings();

let currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
let currentMonth = new Date().getMonth();
let selStart = null, selEnd = null, hoverDate = null, selectingEnd = false;

const MONTHS_DA = ['Januar','Februar','Marts','April','Maj','Juni','Juli','August','September','Oktober','November','December'];

function dateStr(d) { return d.toISOString().split('T')[0]; }

function dateDiff(a, b) {
  return Math.round((new Date(b) - new Date(a)) / 86400000);
}

function isOccupied(str) { return occupiedDates.has(str); }

function isPast(y, m, d) {
  const today = new Date(); today.setHours(0,0,0,0);
  return new Date(y, m, d) < today;
}

function isToday(y, m, d) {
  const t = new Date();
  return t.getFullYear() === y && t.getMonth() === m && t.getDate() === d;
}

function inRange(str) {
  if (!selStart) return false;
  const ref = selectingEnd && hoverDate ? hoverDate : selEnd;
  if (!ref) return false;
  const [s, e] = selStart <= ref ? [selStart, ref] : [ref, selStart];
  return str > s && str < e;
}

function renderCalendar() {
  const title = document.getElementById('calTitle');
  title.innerHTML = MONTHS_DA[currentMonth] + ' <span>' + currentYear + '</span>';
  const grid = document.getElementById('calDays');
  grid.innerHTML = '';

  const firstDay = new Date(currentYear, currentMonth, 1).getDay();
  const offset = (firstDay + 6) % 7;
  const daysInMonth = new Date(currentYear, currentMonth + 1, 0).getDate();

  for (let i = 0; i < offset; i++) {
    const el = document.createElement('div');
    el.className = 'cal-day empty';
    grid.appendChild(el);
  }

  for (let d = 1; d <= daysInMonth; d++) {
    const str = currentYear + '-' + String(currentMonth+1).padStart(2,'0') + '-' + String(d).padStart(2,'0');
    const el = document.createElement('div');
    el.className = 'cal-day';

    const past = isPast(currentYear, currentMonth, d);
    const occ = isOccupied(str);

    if (past) { el.classList.add('past'); }
    else if (occ) { el.classList.add('occupied'); }
    else { el.classList.add('free'); }

    if (isToday(currentYear, currentMonth, d)) el.classList.add('today');
    if (str === selStart) el.classList.add('selected-start');
    if (str === selEnd) el.classList.add('selected-end');
    if (inRange(str)) el.classList.add('selected-range');

    const inner = document.createElement('span');
    inner.className = 'day-num';
    inner.textContent = d;

    if (!past) {
      const dot = document.createElement('span');
      dot.className = 'day-dot ' + (occ ? 'dot-occupied' : 'dot-free');
      inner.appendChild(dot);
    }

    el.appendChild(inner);

    if (!past && !occ) {
      el.addEventListener('click', () => onDayClick(str));
      el.addEventListener('mouseenter', () => { hoverDate = str; renderCalendar(); });
      el.addEventListener('mouseleave', () => { hoverDate = null; renderCalendar(); });
    }

    grid.appendChild(el);
  }
}

function onDayClick(str) {
  if (!selStart || (selStart && selEnd)) {
    selStart = str; selEnd = null; selectingEnd = true;
  } else if (selectingEnd) {
    if (str < selStart) { selEnd = selStart; selStart = str; }
    else { selEnd = str; }
    selectingEnd = false;
    // Check no occupied dates in range
    let d = new Date(selStart);
    const endD = new Date(selEnd);
    let hasOcc = false;
    while (d <= endD) {
      if (isOccupied(d.toISOString().split('T')[0])) { hasOcc = true; break; }
      d.setDate(d.getDate() + 1);
    }
    if (hasOcc) { alert('Perioden indeholder optagede datoer. Vælg venligst en anden periode.'); selStart = null; selEnd = null; }
  }
  renderCalendar();
  updateForm();
}

function formatDate(str) {
  if (!str) return null;
  const [y, m, d] = str.split('-');
  return d + '/' + m + '/' + y;
}

function calcPrice(days) {
  if (days === 1) return PRICES[1];
  if (days === 2) return PRICES[2];
  return PRICES[2] + (days - 2) * PRICE_EXTRA;
}

function updateForm() {
  const sb = document.getElementById('startDateBadge');
  const eb = document.getElementById('endDateBadge');
  const hint = document.getElementById('daysHint');
  const summary = document.getElementById('bookingSummary');
  const btn = document.getElementById('submitBtn');

  if (selStart) {
    sb.textContent = formatDate(selStart);
    sb.classList.add('has-date');
  } else {
    sb.textContent = 'Vælg startdato';
    sb.classList.remove('has-date');
  }
  if (selEnd) {
    eb.textContent = formatDate(selEnd);
    eb.classList.add('has-date');
    const days = dateDiff(selStart, selEnd) + 1;
    const price = calcPrice(days);
    hint.textContent = days + (days === 1 ? ' dag valgt' : ' dage valgt');
    summary.style.display = 'block';
    document.getElementById('summaryDays').textContent = days + (days === 1 ? ' dag' : ' dage');
    document.getElementById('summaryType').textContent = days <= 2 ? MONTHS_DA[0] + '-pakke' : 'Fleredages leje';
    document.getElementById('summaryPrice').textContent = 'kr. ' + price.toLocaleString('da-DK');
    btn.disabled = false;
    btn.textContent = 'Send bookingforespørgsel';
  } else if (selStart) {
    eb.textContent = 'Vælg slutdato';
    eb.classList.remove('has-date');
    hint.textContent = 'Klik nu på slutdatoen';
    summary.style.display = 'none';
    btn.disabled = true;
    btn.textContent = 'Vælg slutdato for at fortsætte';
  } else {
    eb.textContent = 'Vælg slutdato';
    eb.classList.remove('has-date');
    hint.textContent = 'Klik på en startdato i kalenderen';
    summary.style.display = 'none';
    btn.disabled = true;
    btn.textContent = 'Vælg datoer for at booke';
  }
}

// Month navigation
document.getElementById('prevMonth').addEventListener('click', () => {
  currentMonth--; if (currentMonth < 0) { currentMonth = 11; currentYear--; }
  renderCalendar();
});
document.getElementById('nextMonth').addEventListener('click', () => {
  currentMonth++; if (currentMonth > 11) { currentMonth = 0; currentYear++; }
  renderCalendar();
});

// Submit
document.getElementById('submitBtn').addEventListener('click', () => {
  const name = document.getElementById('fullName').value.trim();
  const email = document.getElementById('email').value.trim();
  const phone = document.getElementById('phone').value.trim();
  const addr = document.getElementById('address').value.trim();

  if (!name || !email || !phone || !addr) {
    alert('Udfyld venligst alle obligatoriske felter: navn, telefon, e-mail og adresse.');
    return;
  }
  if (!selStart || !selEnd) return;

  saveBooking(selStart, selEnd);

  const ref = 'VB-' + Math.random().toString(36).substr(2,6).toUpperCase();
  document.getElementById('modalRef').textContent = ref;
  document.getElementById('modalEmail').textContent = email;
  document.getElementById('modalOverlay').classList.add('open');

  // Reset
  selStart = null; selEnd = null; selectingEnd = false;
  document.getElementById('fullName').value = '';
  document.getElementById('phone').value = '';
  document.getElementById('email').value = '';
  document.getElementById('address').value = '';
  document.getElementById('message').value = '';
  renderCalendar();
  updateForm();
});

document.getElementById('modalClose').addEventListener('click', () => {
  document.getElementById('modalOverlay').classList.remove('open');
});

// Init
renderCalendar();
updateForm();
</script>
</body>
